ToxiProxy

A Perl client for ToxiProxy (https://github.com/Shopify/toxiproxy).

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

        carton install 

        ...or the default way...

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc ToxiProxy

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=ToxiProxy

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/ToxiProxy

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/ToxiProxy

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/ToxiProxy/


